import React from 'react'

import { BrowserRouter, Route, Router } from 'react-router-dom'

import Home from './pages/Home'
import CGV from './pages/CGV'
import Megabox from './pages/Megabox'
import CineQ from './pages/CineQ'
import Serieson from './pages/Serieson'
import Moviechart from './pages/Moviechart'

const App = () => {
    return (
        <BrowserRouter>
            <Router>
                <Route pate='/' element={<Home />} />
                <Route pate='/CGV' element={<CGV />} />
                <Route pate='/MegaBox' element={<Megabox />} />
                <Route pate='/CineQ' element={<CineQ />} />
                <Route pate='/Serieson' element={<Serieson />} />
                <Route pate='/Moviechart' element={<Moviechart />} />
            </Router>
        </BrowserRouter>
    )
}

export default App
